<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-62-0900 </DOCNO><TEXT>The evaluation of the technological status and experiences of the solarthermoelectrical power systems is presented in this paper. An economicalassessment is made, showing that big plants have the possibility of beingcompetitive with conventional systems with today's technology. Furtherimprovements from the current R and D programs could bring them intothe market.</TEXT></DOC>